title: Start
body:
John: Your alive Jane
Jane: Honey its so good to see your okay
John: why aren't the kids with you, i found timmy in the basement. And i found Tom out the back
Jane: i needed to make sure i was safe, i couldnt find them and i wasnt about to die trying
John: Tom is dead,he is fucking dead and you are hiding up here, you were meant to keep them safe.
Jane:Im not their mother, im just the step-mum. why would i risk my life for them.
John: I'm done with u jane, we are over.I'm grabbing Timmy and we are out of here.
Jane: you'r not leaving me john, not now not ever."pulls gun on John"
John: jane were did u get the gun from, dont do something crazy
Jane: Your not leaving
[[Jane Im leaving |leaving]]
[[ pull gun on Jane |gun]]

title: leaving
body:

" Jane shoots john in the back"

John: " cough blood" please Jane keep Timmy safe
"The light leaves Jane's eyes when she sees what she has done "
Jane: you said Timmys in the basement right. you took yourself away from me, so I'm going to take Timmy away from u

title: gun
body:

"Jane starts crying and aims the gun at John"
Jane: this is your last chance John we are leaving together
